properties.name: kms.url
properties.description: Kurento Media Server ip and entrypoint, e.g., http://0.0.0.0:8888/kurento

properties.name: turn1.internal.sever
properties.description: TURN server ip from AP (usually LAN IP), e.g., 0.0.0.0:3478?transport=udp

properties.name: turn1.server
properties.description: TURN server ip from user (usually public IP), e.g., 111.111.111.111:3478?transport=udp

properties.name: turn2.internal.sever
properties.description: TURN server ip from AP (usually LAN IP), e.g., 0.0.0.0:3478?transport=udp

properties.name: turn2.server
properties.description: TURN server ip from user (usually public IP), e.g., 111.111.111.111:3478?transport=udp

properties.name: turn.static-auth-secret
properties.description: CoTURN static-auth-secret parameter, used for user authentication

properties.name: objdet.default.confidence
properties.description: default confidence for filtering output objects; should be 0.1~0.9

properties.name: objdet.default.boxlimit
properties.description: default objects maximum output number; should be 1~100

properties.name: objdet.default.drawbox
properties.description: default value for drawing objects on the stream or not

properties.name: objdet.detectedbox.speed.millisec
properties.description: default value for inference delay between frames; should be 100~2000

properties.name: objdet.detectedbox.distinct
properties.description: whether to combine similar objects between frames or not

properties.name: objdet.detectedbox.distinct.ratio
properties.description: threshold for combining similar objects; how close of two objects in ratio is treated as identical object; should be 0.001~0.9
